  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>. This intimidating fighter craft is exceptionally maneuverable, its <span class=\"name name-technology\">Flight Assist Override</span> technology enabling it to deftly drift between celestial bodies.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>。这艘令人胆怯的战斗飞船拥有着极致的机动能力，搭载的<span class=\"name name-technology\">超控飞行协助</span>技术使得飞船能够在星体之间迅捷游走。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>。這艘令人生畏的戰鬥機，操控性十分靈活，<span class=\"name name-technology\">飛行輔助覆寫</span>科技使其能夠快速在星體之間穿梭。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，可以利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
